1. The Historical Training Data Problem (Critical Architecture Gap)
The proposal says "train on historical normal data." This sounds simple but is architecturally complex for Dhara. Your profile_snapshot_store.py stores statistics — not raw rows. PyOD/COPOD cannot train on statistics.

